                    <strong>Weekly Updates:</strong> Progress reports, photos, schedules
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                  <div>
                    <strong>Budget Tracking:</strong> Cost reports, change order management
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">✓</span>
