              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Initial Consultation</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Site visit, scope definition, preliminary budget, timeline discussion. Free consultation and estimate.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
