                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Contract & Mobilization</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Fixed price contract, payment schedule, mobilize equipment and crew, establish site logistics.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                4
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Construction Phase</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Execute work plan, coordinate trades, daily quality control, weekly progress meetings.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                5
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Quality Control</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Stage inspections, code compliance verification, deficiency correction, client walkthrough.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                6
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Project Completion</h3>
